### [Ezekiel Chapter 4](../../../bib/kjv/eze004.htm#001.md)

[Ezekiel](../../../bib/kjv/eze001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">eze 4:0</span></span>

Overview

[Eze 4:1](../../../bib/kjv/eze004.htm#001.md), Under the type of a siege is
shewn the time from the defection of Jeroboam to the captivity; [Eze
4:9](../../../bib/kjv/eze004.htm#009.md), By the provision of the siege, is
shewn the hardness of the famine.

